30
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,390
Three Principles of the People

31
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,720
as the guiding ideology

32
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:26,920
of the revolutionary movement,

33
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,390
but they were not accepted.

34
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,920
So he's very disappointed.

35
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,520
Is that so?

36
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,490
No wonder he's been quiet

37
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:40,000
and snapping at me all the time.

38
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:43,310
Snapping at you is nothing.

39
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:45,159
He even had a huge fight with me.

40
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,590
That's just how he is.

41
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,810
Feeling the entire world is corrupt
and he's clean alone.

42
00:04:48,810 --> 00:04:50,100
You should talk to him.

43
