He feels upset.

44
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,870
This is a matter of ideological differences and
theoretical differences.

45
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,670
Do you think talking would work?

46
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:59,409
Why are there even differences
between you two?

47
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,330
It really is like that saying,

48
00:05:01,330 --> 00:05:02,860
"When it rains, it pours."

49
00:05:04,450 --> 00:05:05,960
It's revolution after all.

50
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,160
It's not that easy.

51
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:10,510
Shuhong.

52
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,160
I'm here today

53
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,390
to say goodbye to you.

54
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:15,160
I'm going back to China.

55
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,860
The Alliance is about to be established.

56
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,420
My work here is done.

57
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,320
You're leaving too?

58
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,540
What do you mean? Who else is leaving?

59
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,510
Which city are you going back to,

60
