I asked her to rent a storefront there,

63
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,630
so that she could have a job cover

64
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:34,300
like you do.

65
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:36,670
Alright, go.

66
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:37,830
You all go.

67
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:40,470
Once you're all gone, it'll be peaceful.

68
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:46,000
You should still try to understand him.

69
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,270
Tianbai is a sensitive man.

70
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,420
He has a pure heart.

71
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,000
Among the party members,

72
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,390
few possess such outstanding talent

73
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,510
as he does.

74
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,290
Tell him that

75
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,600
all of us members still

76
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:59,570
respect him

77
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,080
and trust him as always.

78
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:03,270
Although we have some different opinions,

79
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,330
it doesn't matter.

80
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,310
You two should

81
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,830
take care of yourselves

82
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,230
and live your life well.

83
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:11,730
I only have one task

84
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,120
for you, Shuhong,

85
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,400
which is to take good care of
Tianbai for me.

86
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:17,830
He doesn't care about the consequences

87
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:20,120
at all when he gets impulsive.

88
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,800
It's good to have you by his side.

89
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,040
At least

90
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,980
he could act like a normal person.

91
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,570
Just like you said,

92
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:29,680
some are responsible for the revolution,

93
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,540
and some are responsible
for the revolutionaries.

94
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:41,040
Cheers!

95
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,630
Liang Xiang.

96
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,750
Congratulations.

97
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,090
Liang Xiang.

98
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,750
Is this

99
00:07:04,210 --> 00:07:05,270
the "Golden Straw"

100
