00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,790
You look handsome, Kaizhi.

252
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:37,530
This Japanese military uniform

253
00:15:37,530 --> 00:15:38,970
feels really awkward to wear.

254
00:15:38,970 --> 00:15:40,030
Many people here in Tokyo

255
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:41,720
think I just came back from the front line.

256
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,080
You know, at a time like this,

257
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,670
why should we get involved in this mess?

258
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:46,270
That's right. We shouldn't.

259
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:47,750
It's dog-eat-dog.

260
00:15:48,190 --> 00:15:49,790
Some people naively believe

261
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,360
that Japan's victory over Russia

262
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,240
was a triumph of constitutional monarchy

263
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,370
over dictatorship.

264
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:56,630
Ridiculous. How ridiculous.

265
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,160
Make yourself at home.

266
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:01,970
Shuhong!

267
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,930
Kaizhi is here. Pour some tea.

268
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:07,230
What's your take on this, Mr. Wu?

269
00:16:07,230 --> 00:16:08,630
News from China reports that

270
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:11,030
Yuan Shikai and others have suggested that

271
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,840
the court learn from Japan and

272
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,520
implement a constitutional government.

273
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,640
You want to know

274
00:16:15,670 --> 00:16:16,530
my take on this?

275
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,510
Yes.

276
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,360
Listen, Yang Kaizhi.

277
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:22,130
Let those idiots waste their time.

278
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,260
Let's see who'll have the last laugh.

279
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:26,600
They think there will be no revolution after
the constitution is established?

280
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,200
Nonsense!

281
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,780
If we don't establish a constitution,
we will overthrow it.

282
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:30,360
If we establish a constitution,

283
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,750
we will still overthrow it.

284
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:33,360
Not to mention constitutional monarchy.

285
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,790
Mr. Wu, your theories have always been

286
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:36,520
so straightforward and clear.

287
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:37,960
